              "content": "<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" style="min-width: 100%; " class="stylingblock-content-wrapper"><tr><td class="stylingblock-content-wrapper camarker-inner"><br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Now is the time to get the NSU EDGE and add value to your career!<br>
<br>
The Master of Science in Law Programs are designed for professionals to complete their course work entirely online and you can finish the program in 2 years or less. We do not require a GRE or LSAT to apply and you may qualify for Financial Aid!<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><div style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><b>There are 4 programs to choose from:</b></span></span></div><div style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Education Law<br>
	Employment Law<br>
	Health Law<br>
	Law &amp; Policy<br>
	<span style="background-color:#ffff33;">Learn about our FAST TRACK to complete the degree in 1 year!</span></span></span></div><br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Attend the information session and learn all about program details and I will give you a <b>$50 waiver code</b> for the application!<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><div style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><b>Upcoming semesters for 2022:</b><br>
	Spring April 4<br>
	Summer June 27<br>
	Fall September 26</span></span></div><br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><u>Click on a link below to register for an Information Session:</u>&nbsp;<br>
Feb 17, 2022 10:00 AM Eastern Time (US and Canada)&nbsp;<br>
Register in advance for this meeting:<br>
<a alias="https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJ0tf--uqzspH9VVCgb5CASFvmmaV7CAMtat" conversion="false" data-linkto="https://" href="https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJ0tf--uqzspH9VVCgb5CASFvmmaV7CAMtat" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJ0tf--uqzspH9VVCgb5CASFvmmaV7CAMtat">https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJ0tf--uqzspH9VVCgb5CASFvmmaV7CAMtat</a><br>
<br>
<br>
Can&rsquo;t attend the session but still interested? Schedule a meeting directly with me by clicking here &nbsp;</span></span><b><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><a alias="Schedule a time to speak" conversion="false" data-linkto="https://" href="https://calendly.com/nsulaw" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="Schedule a time to speak">Schedule a time to speak</a></span></span></b><br>
<br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Please contact me with any questions.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
<span style="color:#000099;"><b>Elizabeth DiBiase, MS</b></span><br>
&nbsp;<br>
<i>Assistant Director II Graduate and Online Programs</i><br>
&nbsp;<br>
Shepard Broad College of Law<br>
&nbsp;<br>
Office (954) 262-6367<br>
&nbsp;<br>
<a alias="ed400@nova.edu" conversion="false" data-linkto="mailto:" href="mailto:ed400@nova.edu?subject=" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="ed400@nova.edu">ed400@nova.edu</a> | <a alias="https://www.law.nova.edu/online" conversion="false" data-linkto="https://" href="https://www.law.nova.edu/online/" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="https://www.law.nova.edu/online">https://www.law.nova.edu/online</a></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><b><a alias="Schedule a time to speak" conversion="false" data-linkto="https://" href="https://calendly.com/nsulaw" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="Schedule a time to speak">Schedule a time to speak</a></b></span></span><br>
