              "content": "<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" style="min-width: 100%; " class="stylingblock-content-wrapper"><tr><td class="stylingblock-content-wrapper camarker-inner"><br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Now is the time to get the NSU EDGE and add value to your career!<br>
<br>
The Master of Science in Law Programs are designed for professionals to complete their course work entirely online and you can finish the program in 2 years or less. We do not require a GRE or LSAT to apply and you may qualify for Financial Aid!<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><div style="text-align: center;">
 <span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><b>There are 4 programs to choose from:</b></span></span></div><div style="text-align: center;">
 <span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Education Law<br>
 Employment Law<br>
 Health Law<br>
 Law &amp; Policy</span></span></div><div style="text-align: center;">
 <span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="background-color:#ffff66;">Learn about our FAST TRACK to complete the degree in 1 year!</span></span></span></div><br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Attend the information session and learn all about program details and I will give you a <u><b>$50 waiver code</b></u> for the application!<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><div style="text-align: center;">
 <span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><b>Upcoming semesters for 2022:</b></span></span></div><div style="text-align: center;">
 <span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Summer June 27<br>
 Fall September 26</span></span></div><br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><u>Click on a link below to register for an Information Session:</u>&nbsp;</span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">April 19, 2022 12:00 PM Eastern Time (US and Canada)&nbsp;<br>
Register in advance for this meeting:<br>
<a alias="https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJEsce6spzouEtOcqzOHwkEH9hiAxnnzZktn" conversion="false" data-linkto="https://" href="https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJEsce6spzouEtOcqzOHwkEH9hiAxnnzZktn" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJEsce6spzouEtOcqzOHwkEH9hiAxnnzZktn">https://nova.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJEsce6spzouEtOcqzOHwkEH9hiAxnnzZktn</a></span></span><br>
<br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Can&rsquo;t attend the session but still interested? &nbsp;Schedule a meeting directly with me by clicking here&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><b><a alias="Schedule a time to speak" conversion="false" data-linkto="https://" href="https://calendly.com/nsulaw" style="text-decoration:underline;" title="Schedule a time to speak">Schedule a time to speak</a></b></span></span><br>
<br>
<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Please contact me with any questions.</span></span><br>
